@startuml user-interaction-flow
title User Interaction Flow
actor User
participant "User Interface\n(Web or Mobile)" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Backend Platform\nServices" as Backend
participant "AI Intelligence\nPlatform" as AI

User -> UI : User action
UI -> Gateway : Request
Gateway -> Backend : Routed request
Backend -> AI : Analytical request
AI --> Backend : Recommendation or insight
Backend --> Gateway : Response
Gateway --> UI : Response
UI --> User : Display result
@enduml
